      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0356P0_20001109_WH_39'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-burnett' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0356P0_20001109_WH_39' title='Link to this speech by Mr John Burnett' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-john-burnett" title="Mr John Burnett">Mr. Burnett</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I feel sure that the hon. Gentleman did not mean to omit it but, for completeness, I am certain that he will agree that the Council of Licensed Conveyancers should also be drawn into the regime.
          </p>
